	<text xml:lang="la">
		<body>
			<div>
				<p>
					<s n="1" xml:lang="la" type="auto">S. D.</s>
					<s n="2" xml:lang="la" type="auto">Iuvenem hunc, compater in domino charissime, quem scholarchę nostri ad scholam vestram literis bonis et sacris instituendum mittunt, ego quoque fidei et humanitati tę commendo, quandoquidem illius profectus, quatenus ex auditoribus meis est, et ecclesiae dei destinatur, etiam mihi cordi est.</s>
					<s n="3" xml:lang="la" type="auto">Scimus vestram isthic diligentiam et sedulitatem, de qua nemo nostrum haesitat; attamen facimus, quod nostri est officii.</s>
				</p>
				<p>
					<s n="4" xml:lang="la" type="auto">Domus mea incipit per gratiam domini paululum recreari post uxoris gravissimum casum et fere extremam debilitationem.</s>
				</p>
				<p>
					<s n="5" xml:lang="la" type="auto">Subinde visitamur a domino et castigamur, morti tamen non tradimur; qui percutit, vicissim percussos consolatur; cui sit gloria in sempiternum.</s>
				</p>
				<p>
					<s n="6" xml:lang="la" type="auto">De concilio <placeName type="citizen_name" ref="l1107" cert="high">Tridentino</placeName> scribitur ad me ab amicis <placeName ref="l18" cert="high">Augustanis</placeName> esse suspensum ad menses aliquot; utinam laqueus ille, quo suspensum est, nunquam solvatur.</s>
				</p>
				<p>
					<s n="7" xml:lang="la" type="auto">De Caesare nemo ex <placeName ref="l18" cert="high">Augustanis</placeName> ne verbum quidem significat.</s>
					<s n="8" xml:lang="la" type="auto">Principem, filium illius, ferunt 19. mensis huius <placeName ref="l18" cert="high">Augustam</placeName> egressum, ut <placeName type="citizen_name" ref="l834" cert="high">Italiam</placeName> peteret indeque in <placeName type="citizen_name" ref="l875" cert="high">Hispaniam</placeName> abiret, verum vix unius diei itinere confecto confestim <placeName ref="l18" cert="high">Augustam</placeName> esse reversum.</s>
					<s n="9" xml:lang="la" type="auto">Causa ignoratur; divinant aliqui impeditum esse a classe <placeName type="citizen_name" ref="l2510" cert="high">Turcica</placeName>, ne per <placeName ref="l1121" cert="high">Genuam</placeName> in <placeName type="citizen_name" ref="l875" cert="high">Hispaniam</placeName> traiicere posset, alii nescio quo illum morbo subito correptum esse dicunt.</s>
					<s n="10" xml:lang="la" type="auto">De <placeName type="citizen_name" ref="l303" cert="high">Magdeburgensibus</placeName> nihil hic certi habemus.</s>
					<s n="11" xml:lang="la" type="auto">Literas amicorum <placeName type="citizen_name" ref="l18" cert="high">Augustanorum</placeName> <placeName type="citizen_name" ref="l586" cert="high">Zurzaccum</placeName> allatas nondum accepi; cui concreditae sunt, inclusit eas vasculo, quod nondum est allatum.</s>
					<s n="12" xml:lang="la" type="auto">Si quid ex illis novi ac certi accepero, communicabo.</s>
					<s n="13" xml:lang="la" type="auto" ana="farewell">Optime vale, compater in domino charissime.</s>
					<s n="14" xml:lang="la" type="auto" ana="salute">Salutant te ac domum tuam mei omnes.</s>
					<s n="15" xml:lang="de" type="manual"><foreign xml:lang="la">Filiolus tuus <persName type="citizen_name" ref="p2207" cert="high">Iohannes Heinricus</persName> incipiens garrire nihil adeo frequens in ore habet atque</foreign> "du Schwab;" er will kein Schwab seyn, schwabet die andern kinder alle.</s>
					<s n="16" xml:lang="la" type="auto" ana="salute">Salutem dominis et fratribus, d. <persName ref="p8171" cert="high">Theodoro Bibliandro</persName>, <persName type="citizen_name" ref="p8011" cert="high">Rudolfo</persName>, <persName ref="p8127" cert="high">Pellicano</persName> et <persName cert="high" type="citizen_name" ref="p506">Butlero</persName>.</s>
					<s n="17" xml:lang="de" type="auto"><placeName ref="l41" cert="high">Bernę</placeName> 30. maii 1551.</s>
				</p>
				<p>
					<s n="18" xml:lang="la" type="auto"><persName ref="p8417" cert="high">W[olfgangus] Musculus</persName>, compater tuus in domino.</s>
					<s n="19" xml:lang="la" type="auto">Celeberrimo theologo m. <persName ref="p495" type="citizen_name" cert="high">Heinrycho Bullingero</persName>, <placeName ref="l587" type="auto_name" cert="high">Tigurinę</placeName> ecclesię pastori vigilantissimo, compatri suo in domino charissimo.</s>
					<s n="20" xml:lang="la" type="auto"><placeName ref="l587" type="auto_name" cert="high">Tiguri</placeName>.</s>
				</p>
			</div>
